lang=EN-US>14 </SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>1 </SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1 
</SPAN>日的公允价值。甲商业银行应当按<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>×<SPAN lang=EN-US>14 
</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>1 </SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1 
